      "id": "cmn1w4t32000eic9fmuta2vjr",
      "title": "The Magic Banya check-in & undress",
      "summary": "Last year our Banya check-in was cramped. This year we wish to help the flow of the greeting and dressing/undressing station much better. ",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 0,
