      "id": "cmnujh6kc00041gxcbscwerdq",
      "title": "Safe walk-way platforms near the Sunny Hills waterfront (Magic Banya)",
      "summary": "Safe, low-built flooring and walkways transform uneven, hazardous ground into stable, well-lit paths—improving flow, safety, and space for co-creation.",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 0,
      "percentageFunded": null,
      "minGoal": 0,
      "maxGoal": 0,
      "income": 0,
      "images": [
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775948375/dreams/ntkbg8skg7mret8hmqdo.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775948577/dreams/xxgeybemz7txy4cmns9f.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775948569/dreams/ke2c8c1wsj394y0mgdrh.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775948585/dreams/rc6aeru2hrmerjkj2bll.jpg"
        }
      ],
      "customFields": [
        {
          "value": "## **Flooring & Walkways: Safety and Flow**\n\nThe terrain on the sunny hills near the water is uneven, with holes that create real safety hazards. Last year, this made movement difficult and at times unsafe.\n\nWe want to prioritize building **stable floor sections and walkways** using wooden pallets or similar solutions. This will improve both **safety and natural flow** between areas.\n\nAdding **lighting** will further ensure visibility in fog and at night.\n\nExpanding safe, stable ground also opens for **greater co-creation**, allowing other projects to join and use the space without risk.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Expected to be battery-powered or solar-powered only.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Coral",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Designated Dr. Bill-Bull (treasurer of the dream)"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Engineers guide safe, load-bearing design. Flooring stays low, stable, and non-slip, not raised. Walkways improve safety on uneven ground, with added lighting for night and fog visibility.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Safety"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "This year, we are in active dialogue with other sauna camps to co-create a shared neighbourhood atmosphere and are collectively trying to enhance the swimming pier area. We are very open to co-create collective safe walk ways across the Sunny Hills water front.\n\n  \nBetter flooring would also help opening our space up to others, like performers and masseurs.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "# **MAGIC BANYA by Mist behavior**\n\nThe banya is a Russian-style **steam sauna**, built as a handcrafted tent structure where heat, steam and ritual come together. Using a borrowed banya, the project was a great success in 2025 and this year we come back by engineering our own Borderland Banya, backed by F33!\n\nWEBSITE:[Magic Banya Camp · Borderland 2026](https://magicbanya.com/)",
          "customField": {
            "name": "This dream belongs to camp:"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "This year, we are in active dialogue with other sauna camps to co-create a shared neighbourhood atmosphere and are collectively trying to enhance the swimming pier area.\n\nWe coexisted well with nearby sound camps with padding last year. We explored collaboration with a massage camp, but space limitations made this not so feasible last ýear. Better flooring would also help opening our space up to others.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "*   Full strike on Sunday, with the final people leaving on Monday\n    \n*   All materials removed and packed down\n    \n*   Storage plan for reuse in future years, as required by F33\n    \n*   Focus on reusable and durable materials\n    \n\nThe project is designed for **continuity and minimal waste**.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Strike plan"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We bring very little sound (chimes/gong) but may collaborate with calm performers.\n\nBetter, safer walk ways are not expected to add any sound.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Sound levels"
          }
        }
      ],
