      "id": "cmnog9k9i0002dstzax3cd6m1",
      "title": "The Naughty Improv Theater - by the Fuckery",
      "summary": "The Naughty Improv Theatre is a workshop and performance space where participants explore erotic storytelling, playful roleplay and spontaneous physical comedy",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 0,
      "percentageFunded": 0,
      "minGoal": 600,
      "maxGoal": 1200,
      "income": 0,
      "images": [
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775556838/dreams/tf2sqbk5stchpmfr183k.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775556846/dreams/axvosrp6cammiiy80njs.jpg"
        }
      ],
      "customFields": [
        {
          "value": "The Fuckery",
          "customField": {
            "name": "This dream belongs to camp:"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "## Picture this: a stage. Some willing bodies. Zero script. Infinite possibilities. Some of them awkward, some of them hilarious, perhaps some genuinely, deliciously naughty.\n\n## The Naughty Improv Theatre is a workshop and performance space where participants explore erotic storytelling, playful roleplay and spontaneous physical comedy — all through the liberating lens of improv theatre. No rehearsals, no shame, no bad ideas (only offers). We use classic improv techniques and exercises (perhaps sometimes with a twist) as scaffolding for something raunchier than your average improv exercise.\n\n## Expect laughter. Expect surprise. Expect to discover that vulnerability and desire are basically the same thing wearing different hats.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "## The Naughty Improv Theatre will be operating inside the main event tent of the Fuckery camp—a broader play space designed with care and consent at its core. We will clearly communicate our operating hours. We aim to harmonize with nearby camps and spaces, avoiding overlap with events that might clash in vibe or volume. We are open only during scheduled times to preserve possibilities for other events and activities within the space.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We operate in alignment with The Fuckery's soundscape and sound levels. This dream will not involve music, but a lot of chatter, probably some laughter and maybe some horny sounds.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Sound levels"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "The space will be held by improv theatre facilitators who will introduce the rules, mediate performances, and ensure a safe, respectful, and welcoming atmosphere. Participation is strictly consensual.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Safety"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "## The Naughty Improv Theatre is built entirely on participation and based on principles of improv theatre, meaning that the participants improvise and act on gut feeling. There is no right or wrong! You don't need acting experience. Experienced facilitators will guide warm-up exercises, consent check-ins, and scene work that ranges from flirtatious to filthy — always at the pace the group sets together. \n\n## You don't need to be sexy. You just need to show up, say yes, and be willing to make a fool of yourself in the most magnificent way possible. However, to make the space as sexy as possible we invite you to dress (or undress!) in a way that brings out your sexiest you.\n\n## This is not a show for passive consumption—it’s an invitation to express, embody, and co-create a bodily, theatrical experience. And for those who want to continue the acting and the embodied experience, they can just stay afterwards for the play night that will begin directly after the theatre workshop.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We build Sat-Monday July 19th-20th and are done with Strike no later than Sunday July 26th.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Strike plan"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "This dream relies on electricity estimations of The Fuckery’s infrastructure, in coordination with the camp team.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "@Mirja is our Dr. Bill-Bull.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Designated Dr. Bill-Bull (treasurer of the dream)"
          }
        }
      ],
