        {
          "value": "Always open for co-creations! I mean it's Borderland, come on and reach out if you wanna talk about some idea or if you wanna get involved in Cinema Pizzaiso!",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We’re bringing our Neapolitan pizza setup, projector, and massive 135-inch screen to create the ultimate food + entertainment experience: **welcome to Cinema Pizzaiso!**\n\nStep inside our cozy, stylish movie salon, designed for comfort and high-end culinary vibes, with small sofa tables perfectly placed for your food and drinks.\n\nScreenings last 45–90 minutes, featuring shorter films or series—no three-hour commitments you’ll regret halfway through. Seats can be booked in advance or grabbed first-come, first-served. Once the show starts, the doors close for latecomers.\n\nWe’re the crew behind the legendary pizza parties on the Hills (2022), by The Lake (2023), at Muumimaa (2024), and the hidden gem Kuchen Luchen (2025). Expect **high-quality VEGAN pizza**, featuring our famed homemade cashew mossarella and wild foraged mushrooms like Chicken of the Woods and yellow chanterelles.\n\nWe’ve got most of what we need to make this dream happen, but we’re asking for your contributions to bring this grand vision to life! **/ XOXO**",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        }
