      "title": "Hot sauna 24/7 returns with a fruit bar!",
      "summary": "Last year we re-located one of the most legendary Saunas to Borderland. From arrival to strike the sauna was on 24/7 serving weary hippies. Lets do it again!",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 0,
