        {
          "value": "When on site will need from the grid for lighting and cords, but will be close to Yggdrasil as a camp also",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We invite anyone that wants to be part of both building the tipi and striking the tipi, even though we will have designated roles for camp build and strike to make sure things run smoothly.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "For the past years, this tipi has sheltered and welcomed many Borderlanders—hosting connection, conversation, and shared moments. Until now, we have rented it. This year, we are seeking support to purchase the tipi and establish it as a permanent presence at Borderland: a lasting space where new beginnings are fostered and memories continue to be made.\n\n  \nWhat’s included: A fully equipped tipi setup, including the tent, wooden benches, fire pit plate, five sheepskins, wild boar skins, and 4–5 mattresses for comfort.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Rooted in Yggdrasil and the Tree of Life, we open the tipi to Borderlanders who wish to host workshops, in dialogue with the event lead. Together, we hold a space of calm and groundedness—inviting connection to mother earth, the land, the light and the summer season .",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        }
