          "value": "# Radical therapist\n\nHave you ever thought: \"Maybe there's something wrong with me. I should probably see a professional, but I don't \"have the time\"\". Or maybe you've made it to the therapist's office but still thought: “I wonder what they really think of me. Am I normal?” Spoiler: The answer is no, you are not normal. You are a perfect storm of your parents shortcomings and your own, of symbolic inner pictures of the anger and lust in your heart, and endless love and acceptance of yourself, deep within the caves of your soul. That storm is the most beautiful and interesting thing about you, if you ask us. Choose on the menu which part of you that you would like to explore first, in a quick but impactful session. Face the most radical, fearless and connected therapists your counciousness could ever dream of.",
