          "value": "We aim to create many self-contained installations (depending on funding), that are relatively small (30cm x 30cm x 10cm). They can be powered by a USB charger where available or have their own batteries. It would be wonderful to have these placed with other camps who may be interested in hosting an installation or in other quiet locations that get some foot traffic.",
