      "id": "cmnw2x4m80004jhn2nk4wh5jt",
      "title": "HYPERCUBE",
      "summary": "experience the mysteries of the hypercube, an animated art installation placed in the middle of the valley",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 0,
      "percentageFunded": 27.77,
      "minGoal": 7200,
      "maxGoal": 12200,
      "income": 2000,
      "images": [
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1776023828/dreams/lcyy6atjskqhpmreajiy.gif"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1776023881/dreams/qsz1lv7uxomxuwgkvmnp.gif"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1776023902/dreams/fkm5enhosyideeeb3s1d.jpg"
        }
      ],
      "customFields": [
        {
          "value": "0",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Sound levels"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Paul Yance - paul.yance@gmail.com",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Designated Dr. Bill-Bull (treasurer of the dream)"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Step into the valley after dark and you'll find something otherworldly that you can't quite make sense of: a row of slender metal frames, each stretched with translucent nylon, standing in formation like the slices of something extra dimensional pulled apart in space.\n\nA projector throws animated light across each slice, visualizing patterns that ripple, pulse, and drift from one sheet to the next. The image doesn't just _land_ on a surface; it hangs in the air between the layers. Each layer of sheer fabric catches its share of the projection, and your eye stitches the rest together. No smoke machines, no haze — just geometry doing the work.\n\nThe effect is something between a hologram, a zoetrope, and a lucid dream. Walk around it and the piece reshapes itself. Stand still and it breathes. Stay a while and the patterns start to feel like they're watching back.\n\n![](https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/v1776026189/dreams/srztiwal9akhjwkload9.png)\n\nHYPERCUBE is an invitation to peek into a different reality and spend a few minutes inside a shape that only exists when the light is on.![](https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/v1776026279/dreams/umvytqtzbjlnlfescs8g.png)",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        }
      ],
      "tags": [],
      "funded": 2000,
      "percentageFundedTrue": 27.78
