      "id": "cmmorp274000tfno8n3jmga5a",
      "title": "Soup Kitchen",
      "summary": "Experience papas vegan meat-a-balls & other dishes of hot, delicious food!\nWe have served food since BL 22, and would LOVE to do so again in 26 🤌",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 1,
      "percentageFunded": 174.41,
      "minGoal": 25800,
      "maxGoal": 44500,
      "income": 45000,
      "images": [
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775743232/dreams/hpailkguqm1616ebgmmp.png"
        }
      ],
      "customFields": [
        {
          "value": "Welcome Home, Darling",
          "customField": {
            "name": "This dream belongs to camp:"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Our surroundings love us because of the food we serve. We are noisy but charming, and our choice of music is perfectly suited for whatever theme we are serving.  \nWe will be serving the food in our Camp, where there will be plenty of space for people to sit and enjoy their time.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "It will be loud, but not outside of the limits of wherever we are placed.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Sound levels"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Asjula on discord - ajuullarsen@gmail.com",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Designated Dr. Bill-Bull (treasurer of the dream)"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We will serve our food in reuseable bowls and will have a team on hand to clean them, so they can be reused for the next group.  \nOur dream will be gone with our camp on sunday.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Strike plan"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We will need all the Power. And our thoughts are simple, we are willing to bribe people to get what we need <3",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "# The Soup Kitchen wants to serve you.\n\nYou might know us. You may have heard Papa offering his **vegan meat‑a‑balls**. Maybe you even tasted our **Welcome Home Dahl-ing?**\n\n### So far, we’ve served more than 1,500 hot, vegan meals during BL.\n\nSame procedure as last year? Of course. As always, we’ll be cooking comforting food for everyone in the early nights of Borderland.\n\n**The Soup Kitchen is an experience.** We care as much about service, interaction, and atmosphere as we do about the food itself.\n\nEvery service is a performance. Last year, Papa Luciano and his sleazy Italian Stallions served their signature polpette al sugo di pomodoro (non‑meat‑a‑balls) while boiling 40 kilos of spaghetti, shouting in Italian, and blasting their favourite canzones.\n\n**What we already have:**\n\n*   A solid kitchen setup with plenty of medium‑sized pots \n    \n*   The necessary know‑how and hygiene courses\n    \n*   Some eating utensils to lend out\n    \n*   _Absolutely no issues with culturally appropriating Italian culture_\n    \n\n**What we need funding for:**\n\n*   Food for 300 pax, 2–3 nights\n    \n*   An big pot + An additional gas burner\n    \n*   A bigger fridge for food storage\n    \n*   Extra utensils \n    \n*   Gas\n    \n*   Transportation",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "If you see yourself serving 300 people in about an hour, all whilst playacting horrible cultural stereotypes then we would love for you to come and join us.\n\nIf you have a dream of cooking a specific meal for all the people of BL, but do not have a proper kitchen setup, then reach out and we can maybe find a time where you can do a pop-up cooking thing. Reach out to Luciano.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We have all the relevant courses and have a bunch of professionals as part of our camp. We follow the fire regulations",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Safety"
          }
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "value": "Experience"
        },
        {
          "value": "Food"
        }
      ],
      "funded": 45000,
      "percentageFundedTrue": 174.42
