          "value": "Three stage workshop.\n\n1.  Theory (yes there is always theory!)\n    \n2.  Demonstration. Nude, yes. If not for the technique come for the glimpse of skin!\n    \n3.  Practise. Couples only. You can hook up at the workshop if you have game and get lucky.\n    \n\nIf we need to explain more you should probably go to the Linedancing workshop instead ;)",
