          "value": "*   Projector: 400W\n    \n*   Laser: 300W\n    \n*   Mixer: 150 W\n    \n*   Speakers: 800W\n    \n*   Fridge: 250W (startup up to 1,2 kW)\n    \n\nTotal: 3 kW",
