      "id": "cmnsw20ds000liglimp1mcapy",
      "title": "The \"Everything is Political\" Chai Stand_2.0",
      "summary": "We are offering homemade chai recipes while intervening on the inevitable, inescapable, and sometimes inconvenient fact that everything is political",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
