      "id": "cmnq7iw0i0006pfcvcs4r78wg",
      "title": "The Orgone Accumulation Research Project",
      "summary": "The Orgone accumulator will unleash massive amounts of inner libido energy. Join the largest experimental research project ever. ",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 1,
      "percentageFunded": 50.8,
      "minGoal": 7775,
      "maxGoal": 20610,
      "income": 3950,
      "images": [
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775852539/dreams/dfe1wy3hvgdvjicwknee.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775662893/dreams/ncya74qghmnnwujlbtar.gif"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775662740/dreams/vgedg4wiw1abdh3ek5en.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775680014/dreams/glqrlwm9jvt79zi1vgyg.jpg"
        }
      ],
      "customFields": [
        {
          "value": "Take your toxic Dur energy elsewhere!",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Mårten Niklasson +4670545424\n\n(send me a text if you want to cocreate)",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Designated Dr. Bill-Bull (treasurer of the dream)"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "The Secret Sailors",
          "customField": {
            "name": "This dream belongs to camp:"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Orgone has never hurt anyone, quite the opposite. It has been used to heal fascists since the early 1900s.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Safety"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Very quiet. We will make announcements with a megafon of sorts. Daytime activity.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Sound levels"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Absolutely! We depend on fellow borderlings to build, use and spread the Orgone. Our minimum budget is for 1 human size accumulator, 1 small size accumulator with shooter and funnel, and one wand. If we get more funding we will build more, and distribute all over the Borderland. Come join us! And please contact us if you want to co-create in any possible weird way. Maybe a dance floor in an Orgonite pyramide.\n\nWe also need study objects for the research project and If there is a researcher that can help write a paper that would be mostly appreciated.\n\nThis is also a service, where Borderlings who feel drained, empty, disillusioned and sad, can come and get embraced by Orgone energy.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "The Orgone will affect everyone in a positive way. Most likely we will have more sunshine and good weather. Probably kids friendly.\n\nDuring day time we are open for collaboration with play spaces by charging their future guests, and their toys, with Orgone.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Will be removed by the end of Borderland. We can disassemble the accumulators for the next BL or the materials will be recycled. We will make minimum alteration of the materials so they may be reused.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Strike plan"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We're bringing Orgone back to the Borderland! Maybe you remember the Orgone toilet in 2015? Now Orgone is accumulating once again. This will be the largest Orgone accumulation project in history. Ancient forgotten civilizations may have done something similar, but the records are annoyingly vague.\n\nOrgone is life force, cosmic energy, present in the atmosphere in free form and concentrated by the accumulator. Wilhelm Reich described it in the 1930s, and while Orgone has since been overshadowed by chi, prana, kundalini, and also sex-negative forces, such as slut shaming and fascism, we believe the time has come for its return.\n\nWe will host an open workshop area where we will construct Orgone accumulators. We have had long and serious studies in the science of Orgone. We will provide drawings, materials, tools, guidance. Once the accumulators are built, we will gather Orgone at Borderland and invite participants to be soaked in it, showered with it, and possibly transformed by it. This is likely a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to expose a large population to Orgone.\n\nIt's a workshop, an experiment, a ritual. A trip into the muddy waters of pseudo-science. It is about rebuilding lost technologies and gathering life positive energy.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        }
      ],
