      "customFields": [
        {
          "value": "Secret Garden",
          "customField": {
            "name": "This dream belongs to camp:"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Packs would have LNT instructions printed onto them.\n\nAltars could be so beautifully displayed that each embassy would want to take them home by the time we're all striking.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Looking to see how feasible it is to design replenishment altars at Saunas, bars, and dancefloors across the savannah.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Ever found yourself at a crossroads that you thought was a one-way street?\n\n*   Reaching deep into your trusted hip-bag at some obscure Muumimaa hour (RIP)\n    \n*   Stumbling out of your sun-blasted tent and headed towards the Blackwater Operations\n    \n*   Still building on Wednesday afternoon, but today the sun is your only companion?\n    \n*   Coming out of the sauna, wondering if you've achieved the epitome of relief?\n    \n\nThe Department of Mineral Affairs would like for you to know that **it now gets even better!**\n\n**Imagine**: balanced hydration, exactly when you need it, wherever you could think of it.\n\nWe are dreaming of establishing **The Chapel of Lost Sodium**, from which we will distribute **replenishment altars** to **electrolyte embassies** across the land.\n\nWe deliver a buffered sodium-forward formula that keeps your enamel safe, your stomach calm, your sphincter undisturbed, and your body blissfully in the middle way.\n\nWe also dream of supplying LNT appropriate stick packs for supreme self-reliance. **(stretch goal,** 1.3-2 SEK materials per pack).",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "value": "Food"
        },
        {
          "value": "Wellness"
        }
      ],
