          "value": "I love film photography and have been doing it at numerous burns since 2016.\n\nConsent is my biggest priority both before taking photos, and before posting them, and often I supply the photos only to the subject. I love that film photography doesn’t take away from immediacy, as you can’t stop what you’re doing at the time to see if you liked the picture.\n\nThis year I would also like to focus on taking more pictures of art without people, which can be used for BL newsletter etc.\n\nAs the price of film has gone up drastically lately, I’d love to have a dream to buy a few more rolls for the burn, otherwise I’ll be restricted in how much I can shoot.\n\nPrevious albums: [2023](https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=oa.1428606011266812&type=3), [2022](https://www.facebook.com/groups/theborderland/permalink/5764547710231281/), [2019](https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=oa.2681777921841624&type=3), [2018](https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=oa.2101578016528287&type=3), [2017](https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=oa.1694010667285026&type=3)\n\n2024 and 2025 are on discord.",
