          "value": "🎨 I want to offer face paintings, and use your bodies as canvases. Does that make me a pimp? Perhaps. Do you feel like your earthly form, aka ride, could use some art on it? Then look no further!\n\n✨ Pimp your ride, pimp your pride ✨\n\n🎨 I'm a painter, and this is my humble dream of giving people at Borderland the feeling of \"yass queen\", to transform themselves into fairies, or simply to surrender themselves to the greater pimp.\n\n(open for co-creations within the theme of pimping all them borderlings)",
