        {
          "value": "We consider this a relatively safe dream with no large or heavy structures. Watch out for brain freeze from the cold drinks - don’t drink too fast!🥶",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Safety"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Strike on Saturday if weather forecast allows. Careful check of **M.O.O.P** on our final day so we leave the place in great condition. Slush machine & seating etc will be cleaned and returned to BL.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Strike plan"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "⚡️ Power will be needed to run our speaker system, DJ table, fridge, drink machines and some lights. ~4000-5000w, we would require 32A 230v.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "**🎼 As a sound-focused dream** we take care to place our little disco haven in a suitable spot where the vibe is buzzing - but still with attention to sound levels, sound direction and wishes from our neighbors. Given a shorter playtime we hope to not disturb any early/late sleepers ;)",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "🍹With a touch of refreshing drinks we invite everyone to share their energy with us to the groovy tracks of our dream. **Maybe you have something tasty that will mix well with our ice-cold drinks?** We invite neighbors and everyone else to enjoy our spot, as a living room to co-exist in whatever energy state you are. Let’s make this Ballroom bliss a cozy and friendly place for connecting and to dance together.\n\n**The fridge & slush machine can be left at BL to allow others to create great chilly dreams in the future**, as well as much of the decorations like shiny pillows and seating.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Get into the groove at Ballroom Bliss with DJ Divanté and DJ Simpqlicious with friends. **Daytime parties with disco, deep house & house classics with refreshing ice-cold drinks.** A daytime session that puts the groove in your heart, smile on your face and makes your feet move while keeping you cool in the summer heat. Welcome to our glamorous & blissfull disco inferno!\n\n**Good times ahead, together as one! ♥️**\n\n**We will serve two flavors of delicious non-alcoholic ice slushies; virgin margarita & virgin strawberry daiquiri!** Enjoy your drink in the shade of our cozy tipi tent ⛺️, or out on the sunny little dancefloor☀️ Together we will create good times together in the summer warmth. **Disco is for everyone!!! Disco is life!! 🪩**\n\nLook for our disco flag raised above our tipi!\n\nWelcome to the Ballroom Bliss.\n\n**Wednesday to Friday between 12-17 somewhere in Highlands**\n\n_(budget spans from \"budget-mode\" of less decorations/glamour and a single flavor slush machine, up to the dual flavored slush machine and a generally more disco-glossy premium experience)_\n\nPs. All the text is 100% written by ourselves to try and convey our dream - no AI (although we did feel AI was helpful for the picture as we are not good at drawing)",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        }
