      "id": "cmnuwpyp4000cngezc92tn814",
      "title": "🍑 Laser Buttplug Games - Borderland Cup 🍑",
      "summary": "From billions of years of evolution to this: humans now play a bonkers future‑sport where lasers fly, robots hustle, and nobody remembers how we got here.",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 0,
      "percentageFunded": 65.73,
      "minGoal": 9256,
      "maxGoal": 14118,
      "income": 6084,
      "images": [
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775952862/dreams/dn9fc7bl6hw8yoxzihjg.png"
        }
      ],
      "customFields": [
        {
          "value": "We’ll clean everything up right after the game so the hall can be used again immediately after the strike.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Strike plan"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We’ll need power for the sound system and the fog machine, and maybe for a few small things like lamps, signs, or a popcorn machine.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Philea Lanar - randriaminahy@gmail.com",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Designated Dr. Bill-Bull (treasurer of the dream)"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "**Players/participiants:** We'll use protection and lubricant, and all players will get a safety briefing.\n\n**Sexually explicit content and nudity:** Closed venue — not visible to the general public.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Safety"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "## The Evolution of Sport\n\nFor four billion years, life on this planet has been reaching toward something. Toward this moment.\n\n### The Vision\n\nSingle cells divided. Fins became legs. Apes descended from the trees and gazed at the stars. Darwin could never have dreamed of this. Einstein theorized it. Now, we play it.\n\n### The Technology\n\nPlayers wield coherent light as their ancestors once wielded spears. Laser-equipped buttplugs guide autonomous robots across the arena in an athletic display of precision and strategy.\n\n### THE TEAMS\n\n3 players per team. One on each side of the field. Each player equipped with a regulation laser buttplug.\n\n### THE ROBOT\n\nThe autonomous ROBO unit has 4 sensors. Hit a sensor with your laser to push the robot in the opposite direction.\n\n### THE OBJECTIVE\n\nGuide the robot across your opponent's end line to score. Highest score after 5 minutes wins.\n\n### THE ARENA\n\n6m x 4m playing field. Smoke-filled for laser visibility. Plexiglass perimeter. Crowds gather close. Full sensory assault.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "It's a one-time event, and we'd love to host it in the machine hall — maybe in the early evening or late afternoon — so the sound stays inside and doesn't bother any neighbors.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We’d love to team up with the camp in the machine hall and use their sound system if that works. The plan is loud music, plus cheering and screaming — but don’t worry, it’s all happening inside.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Sound levels"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We are looking for a space, preferably indoors, and it needs to be dark. We are also looking for a PA system with a microphone for the speaker and a fog machine/hazer. We would love to have cheerleaders and a mascot. We are open to sponsorships 😉 If anyone would like to serve snacks, that would be wonderful.  \nPlease share your ideas, and let’s celebrate our sparkling butts.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        }
      ],
