      "id": "cmnviyy5x000w102i6ehyqk4k",
      "title": "Soirées at Chateau Vadeau",
      "summary": "Daytime soirées with tacos, tea, and soft sounds—come unwind, connect, and drift through gentle rhythms at Chateau Vadeau.",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
