      "id": "cmntav39h000a4m9p9ti75ptz",
      "title": "Pierogi Welcome Feast",
      "summary": "A warm Slavic-inspired community kitchen with Babcia-style hospitality, handmade pierogi, a pickle bar, and open dumpling-making workshops.",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 0,
      "percentageFunded": 33.42,
      "minGoal": 17950,
      "maxGoal": 25745,
      "income": 6000,
      "images": [
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775849389/dreams/hw0p8ldyq2rs3qat50la.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775849401/dreams/wg4hev5pfxaq1d8s2wgq.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775849412/dreams/ypgdjsavh8bjxbvpkj4a.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775849466/dreams/ag7xhi2t8ozqugn3ndg3.jpg"
        }
      ],
      "customFields": [
        {
          "value": "Ada +454418487, Marta +4552222972, Ignacy +48795585666",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Designated Dr. Bill-Bull (treasurer of the dream)"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Things will be kept clean, sober and hygienic. To the best possibilities.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Safety"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We keep the setup simple, so it’s easy to pack down. We strike on Sunday and leave the place better than we found it.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Strike plan"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Hungry people eating kinda soundscape. We’ll be playing some fine slavic tunes too. Nothing too loud and crazy.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Sound levels"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Pierogi bring people together. Pierogi spread love and joy and lets go.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Everyone can come make dumplings with us. No experience needed, we’ll show you how. Join for as long as you want and make sure to be ready to get a bit messy.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Babcia Kamp",
          "customField": {
            "name": "This dream belongs to camp:"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We will need a fair amount of electricity to run 4 electric stoves, a fridge, and some small lighting like fairy lights.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "As you arrive at the borderland universum, follow the scent before you follow the map. Steam rises from bubbling pots... Come closer and you’ll find Her. Babcia (Granny). Arms wide open, ready to feed you better. The kitchen stays open all through Tuesday and we will host workshops: come fold pierogi with us for as long as you desire, or just join us hungry and let others take care of you. We run a pickle bar too!\n\nWonder no more, weary seekers. It’s a place to nourish your tummies and give yourselves a warm grandma embrace. From the lands of hospitable Slavs comes a caravan with ultimate delights: dump-lings of all kinds and shapes, fillings to satisfy your hunger and your soul, pickle bar to acidify your smile and clear your palette for the unexpected kiss. Give yourself and your gut flora those gifts, my friends. \n\nExpect no less than babushkas' love at the counter. Look for colourful aprons, traditional lace and smile wrinkles. We will only charge you up with the dough power and ting-a-ling salty sour filling. Maybe ask you some deep question like only the old and wise ones do. Get you ready for the upcoming adventure, because who embarks on one with empty stomach ey?",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        }
      ],
