          "value": "Everyone will be welcome to come and craft flowers during our flower workshops. And ofc everyone will see the artful flowers and take part of the beautiful messages!\n\n(We are also much for workshops with friendship and connection theme and would love to create that in combination.)\n\nWe would love to be part of a camp to bring flower power!",
