      "title": "Floating swing",
      "summary": "Might make you forget about time and gravity…",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 0,
      "percentageFunded": 90.99,
      "minGoal": 10849,
      "maxGoal": 15339,
      "income": 9872,
      "images": [
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775836968/dreams/uxcmdgcpkwrrybcxpumg.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775836979/dreams/pcaemghqzoa5dywqnsnp.jpg"
        },
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1775836995/dreams/cfnkapbdncluhzxxyfns.jpg"
        }
      ],
      "customFields": [
        {
          "value": "Free camp",
          "customField": {
            "name": "This dream belongs to camp:"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Flying back! (I wish!)\n\nEverything goes back with me",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Strike plan"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Designed by me (Anouck) and I have help from Romain to Build it\n\nContact : anouckoa@gmail.com",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Designated Dr. Bill-Bull (treasurer of the dream)"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "It take some Space! … 6.2metres large, hight is 4m\n\nFor its quiet so it can co-exist with art car, barrio…\n\nIt’s my first time in borderland, so i dont know the topography of the place…\n\nIf you have an idea of the placement, please let me know! :)",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "If someone is inspired to do light display on the wings, that could be amazing!!!!\n\nHappy to have live musicien to make people travel even further!",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "The base is made with heavy steal (40x40x4mm)\n\nExtra U shape ground stake\n\nIf to much wind, easy remouvale of the fabric\n\nThe wings go down at max 2,2m",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Safety"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "No sound or low sound (small speaker or open to live musicien)",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Sound levels"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "According to the budget, LED Lightning is an option for beautiful effect at night time… could be with power or batterie",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Somewhere between a playground and a daydream, this kinetic sculpture invites you to sit, sway… and maybe forget gravity for a while.\n\nDesigned for 1 to 3 people,  the piece takes the familiar language of a swing and teaches it to grow wings.\n\nAbove, vast translucent sails—part butterfly/part underwater creatures/part cosmos dancer—stretch nearly three meters wide, catching light like a whisper of dusk. Their burgundy organza shimmers with violet reflections, as if the sky itself had decided to rest for a moment.\n\nThe structure, grounded in a black metal frame, stands steady and quiet—like a stage waiting for movement.\n\nFrom it, hangs a generous hammock, a shared nest where strangers become companions, and companions become co-pilots. Because this is not just a seat: it’s a collective flight.\n\nWith every motion of the hammock, the bamboo ribs awaken the wings. They do not flap—they breathe. Slow, wide, almost alive. The sculpture listens to the rhythm of its passengers and answers in kind, turning simple play into a choreography of air and balance.\n\nAt nearly four meters tall, it is both an object and an invitation:  \nto gather, to drift, to laugh, to relax and dream\n\nCaution: This is not just a swing, this might be a hippie trap!",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        }
      ],
