        {
          "value": "Burnes Magasin - Rainbow Edition",
          "customField": {
            "name": "This dream belongs to camp:"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Catch the Rainbow Razzle! A rolling rainbow carriage spreading joy across the Playa with vibrant lemonades, magical rainbow lattes, and colorful cuisines. But we're not just about the drinks. Every visitor gets a \"love-spreader\" quest card with a playful mission to connect with someone new. Complete it, find us again, tell us the story and get a sticker, a new quest and level up. The goal? A ripple effect of kindness that reaches way further than our little vehicle ever could.\n\n## **How it works**\n\nWe ride. Slowly, joyfully, through the Borderland, stopping wherever people gather or wherever someone looks like they could use a cold drink, a smile or some love.\n\nEvery person who stops by gets a quest. These are small, playful missions designed into different categories and levels. to break the camp bubble and spark connection between strangers:\n\nWhen you complete your quest, find us again, level up, get a reward sticker and a new quest.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        }
