          "value": "This is a slow-pace workshop where we put strings of feathers into each other's hair - a simple act of care that turns strangers into a co-creators. You get to choose your own colors to fit your amazing outfit, and you can choose to get them attached to a piece of hair permenantly or you can attach the string to a hairpin to take them on/off. The workshop will be held 2 times during the week.",
