          "value": "Voyeur or exhibitionist? Either way — you belong here.\n\nThis is the adult stage of Borderland, brought to you by The Fuckery: a space where daring ideas become live performance, and where the only thing more exciting than being watched… is watching.\n\nGot an x-rated idea? A spicy skit? A bold, barely-there act you've been dying to unleash? Propose it, get on stage, and perform it in front of an audience of curious, open-minded peers. The Fuckery welcomes all ideas — as long as they're juicy enough.\n\n(Prefer to stay in the shadows? Come laugh, gasp, and be thoroughly entertained by your fellow Borderlings' daring attempts.)\n\nThe Erotic Theatre is also the beating heart of The Fuckery's programme, for example:\n\n·       **Fever Night** — a dreamy, live drama performed by The Fuckery team, dripping with allure and intrigue\n\n·       **Fantasy Roleplay showcase** — witness the fruits of collective dark imagination, brought to life on stage\n\n·       **A hotspot for Fuckery play nights** — where unexpected pop-ups happen, and where you can deliberately put yourself center stage, watched by all, while performing your most decadent deeds",
