          "value": "A wise person once said, ” Offering help is kind, asking for help is courageous!” Here we are, old and grumpy, yet very kind, offering you the chance to be courageous!  \n  \nAt Silly Service and Support Spot, we offer anything you like, we have skills that kill and know how to set boundaries and say no. You don’t need to be shy.  \n  \nWe aim to build a (Silly) Sanctuary where you can come when Borderland is too much, your friends are boring or the Sanctuary is too serious. We offer playground and kindergarten-style activities for grown-ups, which you can enjoy by yourself, with a friend or a stranger. We will also offer workshops and talks on many important topics to prepare, strengthen and activate you for this magical and challenging week! And when you most need it, we will serve food and guide yoga and other calming activities. There will be hot and cold beverages in a self-serving bar and a trampoline!",
