      "title": "Sober Psychadelic Light Journey",
      "summary": "The most awesome light experience you’ll ever have\nThe highest you’ll ever be without drugs\nA psychedelic experience and therapy all in one, completely sober",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
