        {
          "value": "A small amount, what is needed to run the lamp and music but not more than a normal lamp.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Last year's big success, now back bigger and better — hopefully with two lamps to meet the high demand!\n\n**Concept:** Ever wanted a psychedelic experience without substances? Camp Nimenoma invites you into a world of mind-bending light and sound with the RoXiva/Dream Machine — your gateway to psychedelic visions, deep relaxation, and limitless creativity. Close your eyes, let colors and patterns carry you to euphoric realms. No substances required. Ready to journey beyond?\n\n**Execution:**\n\n*   Sessions in our cozy camp space, slumber-party style on mattresses.\n    \n*   Headphones paired with the lamp match each programme's frequency, sending you deeper into meditation.\n    \n*   The whole camp sets the mood: hanging lamps, warm lights and glowing details throughout.\n    \n\n**Why it matters:** A fantastic drug-free alternative for mind-expanding experiences, using only light and sound:\n\n*   Psychedelic-like visuals without substances\n    \n*   Brainwave entrainment for optimal mental states\n    \n*   Deep relaxation & stress relief\n    \n*   Euphoria & well-being boost\n    \n*   Reduced mental fatigue & burnout\n    \n*   Heightened creativity & inspiration\n    \n*   Improved focus & mental clarity\n    \n*   Accelerated meditation practice",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        }
