      "id": "cmm0snxdf0000qsigurpwayly",
      "title": "Boob Mobile ",
      "summary": "A Mobile Boob, Sound & Workshop Installation - Dive into an experience, where you explore sound through touch.",
      "status": "IDEA",
      "noOfFunders": 0,
      "noOfComments": 0,
      "percentageFunded": 51.59,
      "minGoal": 16456,
      "maxGoal": 27440,
      "income": 8490,
      "images": [
        {
          "small": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dreamswtf/image/upload/c_scale,q_90,w_740/v1771949042/dreams/hdgq3jiy00wktwc0acli.jpg"
        }
      ],
      "customFields": [
        {
          "value": "We are committed to respecting the wider event environment.\n\nBoob Mobile is mobile and does not permanently occupy space. Sound levels are moderated and adapted to location and time. The installation does not operate continuously and will respect quiet zones and neighboring camps.\n\nClear consent principles are visible and communicated. Interaction is always voluntary, respectful, and inclusive.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-existence"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "We would like to use the local power supply with a connection in the garage of Circus the Analog to charge the batteries.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Electricity"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "🎪 CIRCUS the ANALOG 🎪\n\nBoob Mobile is a collective camp project. It is carried and maintained by the team responsible for technical infrastructure, facilitation, finances, and safety. It grows through shared effort, shared care, and shared responsibility.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "This dream belongs to camp:"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Boob Mobile invites active participation.\n\nPlanned co-creation elements include:\n\n*   Build workshops (papier-mâché sculpting and surface design)\n    \n*   Sound sampling sessions where participants record and contribute sounds\n    \n*   DIY controller building for interactive triggers\n    \n*   Mini-workshops on playful interaction and consent culture\n    \n\nThe installation evolves through contributions from the community. Participants become co-creators rather than spectators.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Co-creation"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "The sound system is designed for playful engagement, not dominance.\n\nThe intention is to have an immersive but not overwhelming sound.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Sound levels"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Safety is central to the project.\n\nVehicle:\n\n*   Roadworthy and mechanically inspected Interaction.\n    \n*   Clear consent culture.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Safety"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "The installation will leave no trace. It will leave the site with us.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Strike plan"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "💕 Hop aboard the Boob Mobile — a cheeky, body-loving art adventure on wheels! This rolling wonder transforms a regular vehicle into a cozy, squishy playground. Two large, soft sculptural forms create an immersive seating and interaction area. Dive into an experience, where you explore sound through touch. Creativity, comfort, and good vibes all packed into one fabulous moving masterpiece!\n\n💕 The nipples function as interactive sound triggers connected to a custom audio system. The vehicle already includes speakers, amplifiers, and a subwoofer, creating a mobile yet contained sonic experience.\n\nDiscover “Boob Diving” … a metaphor that invites participants to dive into softness, humor, sound, and collective experience. The installation combines absurdity, warmth, and empowerment while encouraging reflection on body perception, consent, and shared play.\n\n❣️ Boob Mobile is not about sexualization — it is about reclaiming humor, intimacy, and body symbolism in a conscious and respectful way.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Description"
          }
        },
        {
          "value": "Alenka  \nResponsible for transparent budget handling and financial coordination.",
          "customField": {
            "name": "Designated Dr. Bill-Bull (treasurer of the dream)"
          }
        }
      ],
